dct_title_s: Ward, Lock, & Co.s plan of the city of Paris
dct_description_sm: Shows railways, underground railways, and tramway routes; underground railways routes outlined in green. Probably issued in: A pictorial and descriptive guide to Paris ... London : Ward, Lock and Co., [1905?]
dct_publisher_sm: London : Ward, Lock, & Co., Ltd., Warwick House, Salisbury Square, [ca. 1905] (Edinr. : John Bartholomew & Co.)
